761
00:50:10,590 --> 00:50:15,380
E então eu percebi que, se fosse,

762
00:50:16,550 --> 00:50:18,090
eu queria passar com você.

763
00:50:24,810 --> 00:50:25,640
Tá.

764
00:50:28,480 --> 00:50:29,350
Acho que eu...

765
00:50:31,440 --> 00:50:33,030
